thread.title: No criminal charges filed in death of pop star Prince

title: No criminal charges filed in death of pop star Prince
text:
No criminal charges filed in death of pop star Prince Thursday, April 19, 2018 - 02:09 
Minnesota prosecutor, Mark Metz told a news conference Thursday that no criminal charges will be filed in the 2016 death of pop star Prince from an opioid overdose. Rough Cut (no reporter narration).
